    General Stores in Jogeshwari, Mumbai

    General Stores in Jogeshwari, Mumbai

    Commonly known as 'kiranas' in the local parlance, mom-n-pop shops are nothing but general stores. In marketing terminology, a kirana shop is a form of traditional retail catering to the needs of citizens. In certain metros and cities, a general store can also be a part of a pharmacy or medicine shop. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. General store products comprise of food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Depending on the location of the store  whether in a rural village or an urban metropolis  the stock keeping units or pack sizes of the packaged goods may differ. Certain retail stores have set up their own online store enabling a customer to purchase groceries and other essential products online and have it delivered to the desired address. Please scroll up to find a list of General Stores in Jogeshwari, Mumbai.
